@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Read_More";
}

<div class="slider-container">
    <div class="slider">
        <div class="slider-item">
            <h3><b>Our Story</b></h3>
            <p>
                [Project Name] was founded with the simple goal of tackling one of urban life’s most persistent challenges: parking. With cities becoming more crowded, finding convenient and affordable parking has become increasingly difficult. Recognizing this, our team set out to create a solution that not only simplifies parking but also contributes to the optimization of space and the reduction of congestion in urban areas.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-item">
            <h3><b>Our Approach</b></h3>
            <p>
                We believe that great parking management starts with a clear understanding of the problem. That’s why we combine deep industry knowledge with advanced technology to develop solutions that are not only efficient but also user-friendly. Our systems include features like real-time availability tracking, seamless payment systems, and easy access via mobile applications.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-item">
            <h3><b>Our Team</b></h3>
            <p>
                Our team is a diverse group of experts in technology, operations, urban planning, and customer service. With years of combined experience, we are united by our shared passion for improving the way people interact with their surroundings. We work together to build solutions that are effective, efficient, and scalable, ensuring a positive impact on both individuals and communities.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-item">
            <h3><b>Our Commitment to Sustainability</b></h3>
            <p>
                At [Project Name], sustainability is at the heart of everything we do. We understand that effective parking management can reduce traffic congestion, lower emissions, and make cities more livable. Our solutions are designed to contribute to the sustainability of urban spaces by helping to use resources more efficiently and reduce the carbon footprint of transportation systems.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-item">
            <h3><b>Looking Ahead</b></h3>
            <p>
                As cities evolve, so will we. We're constantly developing new technologies and strategies to make parking smarter and more integrated with other aspects of urban mobility. With a focus on innovation and customer satisfaction, we aim to continue leading the way in parking management solutions for years to come.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Include jQuery and Slick Slider JS -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.js"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        // Initialize Slick Slider
        $('.slider').slick({
            dots: true, // Show dots for navigation
            infinite: true, // Infinite scrolling
            speed: 500, // Transition speed
            slidesToShow: 1, // Show one slide at a time
            slidesToScroll: 1, // Scroll one slide at a time
            autoplay: true, // Auto slide change
            autoplaySpeed: 4000, // Time between auto slides
            pauseOnHover: true, // Pause on hover
        });
    });
</script>

<style>
    /* Slider Container */
    .slider-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    /* Slider Item Styles */
    .slider-item {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: left;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

        .slider-item h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .slider-item p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

    /* Styling the Navigation Dots */
    .slick-dots {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 15px;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .slick-prev, .slick-next {
        background-color: #007BFF !important;
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        line-height: 35px;
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-top: -20px;
    }

        .slick-prev:before, .slick-next:before {
            content: '';
        }

    .slick-dots li button {
        background-color: #007BFF !important;
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .slick-dots li.slick-active button {
        background-color: #0056b3 !important;
    }

    /* Hover Effects */
    .slider-item:hover {
        transform: scale(1.03);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
</style>
